data.description: Fall in love with this fantastic 2-story home with a recent Roof in Rodeo Palms. Upon entering, adore the high-ceiling foyer with polished porcelain tile flooring. A spiral wood staircase sits to your right, next to the half bathroom and the formal dining room to your left. The living room has plenty of natural sunlight with an artic white ledger panel fireplace, which can also be viewed from your granite countertop island kitchen—plenty of cabinet space and a breakfast area. The owner's suite is adjacent to the living room, which offers a fabulous bathroom with dual sinks, a vanity, a separate shower, a jacuzzi tub, and a huge walk-in closet. Upstairs is another bedroom suite with a full bath and walk-in closet. You are separated by a game room and covered balcony from the two guest bedrooms and bathroom. Rodeo Palms offers its residents access to a community pool and clubhouse, Easy access to Pearland, and our very own Manvel Town Center is now in construction.
